Renders property value rows for a SemanticSchemas category display.

Discovers all properties (including inherited) by walking the ancestor
chain via Category/collect-ancestors, then renders a table row for each
property whose value is non-empty on the current page.

Parameter:
* category - The category name (without namespace prefix)
